"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">A simple program that made &quot;Just-for-fun&quot;. It may be useful, for example, athletes, losing weight, or just monitoring their health. It isn\'t Trojan or Barmin\'s patch. When a user attempts to shoot in the leg yourself , it will be resist.</p>\n"
