"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">  Enter name of food, weight in grams and click on &quot;Calculate&quot;. Click on &quot;Autocomlete&quot; will open autocomplete menu (or substitute automatically), click on &quot;Search window&quot; will open search window.</p>\n"
